      • duplicate

        public TupleSerializer<T> duplicate()
        从类复制的说明: TypeSerializer
        Creates a deep copy of this serializer if it is necessary, i.e. if it is stateful. This can return itself if the serializer is not stateful. We need this because Serializers might be used in several threads. Stateless serializers are inherently thread-safe while stateful serializers might not be thread-safe.
        指定者:
        duplicate 在类中 TypeSerializer<T extends Tuple>

      • copy

        public T copy(T from,
              T reuse)
        从类复制的说明: TypeSerializer
        Creates a copy from the given element. The method makes an attempt to store the copy in the given reuse element, if the type is mutable. This is, however, not guaranteed.
        指定者:
        copy 在类中 TypeSerializer<T extends Tuple>
        参数:
        from - The element to be copied.
        reuse - The element to be reused. May or may not be used.
        返回:
        A deep copy of the element.
